        <h3 style="margin-top: 0px;" id="pop_facts">
            Leitchfield Population Facts
        </h3>
    


            <h4>What is the current population of Leitchfield?</h4>
            <p>
                Based on the latest 2022 data from the US census, the
                current population of Leitchfield is 6,409.  Leitchfield, Kentucky is the 4,172nd largest city in the US.
            </p>

            
                <h4>What county is Leitchfield, Kentucky in?</h4>
                <p>
                
                    Leitchfield is located entirely in 
                    Grayson County.
                
                </p>
            

            
                
                    <h4>What is the size of Leitchfield, Kentucky in square miles?</h4>
                    Leitchfield has an area of 
                    10.8 square miles.

                    
                    
                
            

            <h4>What was the peak population of Leitchfield?</h4>
            <p>
                
                    The peak population of Leitchfield was in
                    2010, when its population was
                    6,699.
                    
                        In 2010, Leitchfield was the
                        3,891st largest city in the US; now
                        its fallen to the 4,172nd largest city in
                        the US.
                    
                    Leitchfield is currently
                        <span style="color: red;">
                            4.3%
                            smaller
                        </span>
                        than it was in 2010.
                    </p>
                
            </p>
            
                
                    <h4>How quickly is Leitchfield growing?</h4>
                
                <p>
                    
                        Leitchfield has grown
                        2.8% 
                        since the 2000.
                    


                    
                        Leitchfield, Kentucky's growth is below average.
                        63% of similarly sized
                        cities are growing faster since 2000.
                    
                </p>
            

            

            
                <h4>What is the population density of Leitchfield, Kentucky?</h4>
                <p>
                Leitchfield has a population density of
                617.2 people
                per square mile.

                
                
                </p>
            

            

    
    
        
    

    

    
   
    
