        <h3 style="margin-top: 25px;" id="demographics">
            Leitchfield Demographics
        </h3>
    


            
                

                
                <h4>What is the voting age population of Leitchfield, Kentucky?</h4>
                <p>
                    The total voting age population of Leitchfield, Kentucky, meaning US citizens 18 or older, is 4,872.  The voting age population is 48.2% male and 51.8% female.
                </p>
                

                
                
                    <h4>What percentage of Leitchfield, Kentucky residents are senior citizens?</h4>
                    <p>
                        According to the latest census statistics, 18.2% of
                        the residents of Leitchfield are 65 or older.
                    </p>
                

                
                    

    
    
        
    

    

    
   
    
        <div class="adthrive-content-ad" style="min-height: 120px;">
            
        </div>
    
                    
                    <h4>What are the racial demographics of Leitchfield, Kentucky?</h4>
                    <p>The racial demographics of Leitchfield are 91.7% White, 3.7% Black, 1.7% Other, 1.5% Two or more races and 1.4% American Indian. Additionally, 0.6% of the population identifies as Hispanic.</p>
                

                
                
                    <h4>What percentage of Leitchfield, Kentucky residents are below the poverty line?</h4>
                    <p>
                    In Leitchfield, 26.1% of
                    residents have an income below the poverty line, and the child poverty rate
                    is 40.3%.
                    On a per-household basis,
                    23.8% of families are below
                    the poverty line in Leitchfield.
                    </p>
                

                
                
                    <h4>What percentage of Leitchfield, Kentucky residents are in the labor force?</h4>
                    <p>
                    Among those aged 16 and older, 53.3% of
                    Leitchfield residents are in the labor force.
                    </p>
                

                

    
    
        
    

    

    
   
    
        <div class="adthrive-content-ad" style="min-height: 120px;">
            
        </div>
    

                
                
                <h4>What are the education levels among Leitchfield, Kentucky residents?</h4>
                <p>Among the adult population 25 years old and over,
                    83.7% of
                    Leitchfield residents have at least a high school degree or
                    equivalent, 10.8%
                    have a bachelor's degree and 4.3%
                    have a graduate or professional degree.
                

                
                
                <h4>What percentage of Leitchfield, Kentucky residents speak a non-English language at home?</h4>
                <p>
                Among Leitchfield residents aged 5 and older, 2.3% of them speak a non-English language at home.
                Broken down by language:
                1.1% of residents speak Spanish at home,
                1.2% speak an Indo-European language, and
                0.0% speak an Asian language.

                </p>
                

                
    
        <h3 style="margin-top: 25px;" id="labor">
            Leitchfield Income &amp; Labor Statistics
        </h3>
    


                
                
                    <h4>What is the unemployment rate in Leitchfield, Kentucky?</h4>
                    <p>
                        The unemployment rate in Leitchfield is 2.8%, which is calculated among residents aged 16 or older who are in the labor force.
                    </p>

                

                
                
                    <h4>What percentage of Leitchfield, Kentucky residents work for the government?</h4>
                    <p>
                    In Leitchfield, 12.9% of the
                    residents in the non-military labor force 
                    are employed by the local, state and federal government.
                    </p>
                

                

    
    
        
    

    

    
   
    
        <div class="adthrive-content-ad" style="min-height: 120px;">
            
        </div>
    

                
                
                    <h4>What is the median income in Leitchfield, Kentucky?</h4>
                    <p>The median household income in Leitchfield is $31,221.</p>
                

                
    
        <h3 style="margin-top: 25px;" id="housing">
            Leitchfield Housing &amp; Rent Statistics
        </h3>
    


                
                
                <h4>What percentage of housing units are owner-occupied in Leitchfield, Kentucky?</h4>
                <p>
                    In Leitchfield, 53.3% of housing units
                    are occupied by their owners.
                </p>
                

                
                
                <h4>What percentage of housing units are rented in Leitchfield, Kentucky?</h4>
                <p>
                    Renters occupy 46.7% of housing units in
                    Leitchfield.
                </p>
                

                
                
                    <h4>What percentage of Leitchfield, Kentucky housing units were built before 1940?</h4>
                    <p>
                        Of all the housing units in Leitchfield,
                        2.1% of them were build before 1940.
                    </p>
                

                
                

                
                    <h4>What percentage of Leitchfield, Kentucky housing units were built after 2000?</h4>
                    <p>
                    In Leitchfield, 17.8% of the 
                    total housing units were built
                    
                        after the year 2000, which is approximately 
                        
                            540 units.
                        
                    
                    </p>
                
                
                
                
                <h4>What is the median monthly rent in Leitchfield, Kentucky?</h4>
                <p>
                    The median gross monthly rent payment for renters in Leitchfield is
                    $559.
                </p>

                

                
                
                <h4>What percentage of households in Leitchfield, Kentucky have broadband internet?</h4>
                <p>
                    In Leitchfield, 62.1% of households have
                    an active broadband internet connection.
